{
  "stem": "23090.5",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We had to march.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We had to do-- in fact, as we walked, the dead people had to be picked up by the farmers.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "This was an order by the Germans, that they couldn't leave the bodies.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So each area, each, like, community, or each farm section that we went through, these farmers had to pick them up in these wagons, horse wagons, put the bodies on, and somehow expose of them or eliminate them.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So everybody knew it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "There wasn't a matter of hiding it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that one particular scene with people throwing things, and throwing dirty Jew, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] [GERMAN], and all that kind of thing was just there.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And again, the child situation.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You see no humanity, you see no compassion, you see nothing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You just couldn't-- this thing just continues on, as there is no-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] nothing-- nothing and people to give you some indication there is some heart, some heart there somewhere.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And when we got to Dachau, again, this was a camp of-- not as big as Auschwitz was.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But that, too, was a processing camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And in that camp, I did see some prisoners from-- soldier prisoners.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were captured prisoners.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I think there were some Americans, and British, and so on.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the camp was very, very, very loaded, full with people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we were just hanging around that camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I got to Dachau in '45.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In '45, I would say around April or May of '45.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] And, I tell you, the-- the Bavarian-- the Bavarian winters are just horrendously cold.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, windy, and the only clothes we had was this burlap uniform, was made out of burlap paper, with the little hat.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
